        "Certificate of Undergraduate Study in Diversity & Inclusion in Professional Settings": [
            "Certificate of Undergraduate Study in Diversity & Inclusion in Professional Settings The Certificate of Undergraduate Study (CUGS) in Diversity & Inclusion in Professional Settings deepens understanding about the causes and effects of diversity in the workplace and the potential for subtle bias affecting visible and non-visible minority groups. Valuable skills will be imparted for relating to diverse colleagues and collaborating on intercultural teams. A field placement in one of a variety of career areas provides practical experience observing and applying the principles learned."
        ],
